  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine which of the following drugs: enoxaparin,
      dabigatran and rivaroxaban causes least blood loss after total hip replacement (THR).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
